<headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 27 at 4:56AM EDT  by NWS Blacksburg</headline>
<description>Patchy dense fog has developed this morning, mainly in river and
mountain valleys. Visibilities may be lower than a quarter mile at
times. The fog should begin to lift between 8 and 9 AM. Use
caution when driving and leave plenty of room between cars.</description>
